{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_011HF8huskVNb4iRVP2o4Kk9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's a summary of what was found and fixed:\n\n**Root cause:** The StatefulSet probes had two critical misconfigurations:\n- `timeoutSeconds: 1` — too short for `mongosh` to connect and execute, causing every probe to time out\n- `failureThreshold: 2` — too low, so pods were killed after just 2 back-to-back timeouts (20s window), before MongoDB had a chance to finish starting\n- `initialDelaySeconds` too short (5s readiness, 15s liveness) to allow for normal startup\n\n**Fix applied:** Patched the StatefulSet probes to:\n- `timeoutSeconds: 10` (was 1)\n- `failureThreshold: 6` (was 2)\n- `initialDelaySeconds: 20/60` for readiness/liveness (was 5/15)\n\n**Result:**\n- All 3 pods: `1/1 Running` with 0 restarts\n- **mongodb-replica-1** — PRIMARY\n- **mongodb-replica-0** — SECONDARY\n- **mongodb-replica-2** — SECONDARY"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1212,"cache_read_input_tokens":70612,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1212},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2208e562-ed9b-4743-9e4f-56b62c256165","uuid":"0b83c2ca-8be1-49bc-8fa9-493105735977","request_id":"req_011CcgeU6gUd82nGts9qD2Uw"}
